message.body: We are making a cheese plate and hummus, spanikopita, grilled veggies, herb plate, and caneles with berries and whipped cream for dessert. Sound cool by you?
Ohhhh myyyy god yes. Do you need us to pick up anything? I went to the bottle shop for BOOZE! We plan on leaving Here around 5:45ish
Sweet! We will see you soon!
Thank you guys so much! Hunter says sorry to bust up the party he got fat and tired!
Not at all! So fun having you guys here!
I got fat but not tired.
Hahaha. Me too. Tell Alethia thank you. Have a good night and you guys come over soon.
Awesome. Will do. Maybe I will be able to come to your studio this week.
